rows.label: qst006502_msg0001
rows.name:
So you're Janiki? Give back the
treasure you took from Jamin!

rows.label: qst006502_msg0002
rows.name: What's your problem, lady?

rows.label: qst006502_msg0003
rows.name: L-lady?!

rows.label: qst006502_msg0004
rows.name:
Now, now, just ignore
the brat's ramblings.

rows.label: qst006502_msg0005
rows.name:
Shut up, you tall freak! Don't
act so high and mighty, baldy!

rows.label: qst006502_msg0006
rows.name:
Y-you brat! Who are you
calling baldy?! You've got
some nerve, making me angry!

rows.label: qst006502_msg0007
rows.name:
Anyway! You shouldn't take
things from people! That's no
different from being a thief!

rows.label: qst006502_msg0008
rows.name: Shut up!

rows.label: qst006502_msg0009
rows.name:
If you absolutely refuse to give
it back, then I have no choice.

rows.label: qst006502_msg0010
rows.name: I will use my Overlord's Mind's Eye!

rows.label: qst006502_msg0011
rows.name: Huh?

rows.label: qst006502_msg0012
rows.name: Wh-what's that?!

rows.label: qst006502_msg0013
rows.name:
When I take off this eyepatch,
it identifies bad children and
seals them in this eye!

rows.label: qst006502_msg0014
rows.name:
Hah! You think I'd believe
a lie like that?!

rows.label: qst006502_msg0015
rows.name:
Shall we test if it's a lie?
Don't say I didn't warn you.

rows.label: qst006502_msg0016
rows.name:
...F-fine! I'll give
it back, all right?!

rows.label: qst006502_msg0017
rows.name:
Don't you ever take other
people's things again!

rows.label: qst006502_msg0018
rows.name:
The Overlord's Mind's Eye
is always watching you.

rows.label: qst006502_msg0019
rows.name:
I get it... I'll try
not to do it again...

rows.label: qst006502_msg0020
rows.name:
What the... That's way cooler
than my Overlord's Mind's Eye...
